text: The Ekhagen Church () is a church building at Ekhagen in Jönköping in Sweden. It belongs ot the Kristina-Ljungarum of the Church of Sweden. It was inaugurated on 12 May 1996 by Bishop Anders Wejryd and replaced the former temporary church that stood in Ekhagen between 1968 and mid 1995. ==References== Category:Church of Sweden churches Category:Buildings and structures in Jönköping
title: Ekhagen Church
